{"tid":1947367,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"渾水：格局思維睇手段高明的Boris Johnson","createTime":"2020-03-28T08:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T09:15:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3450b3aecb45c09e9a56a2f55f93e63185daf8a9","tid":1947367,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"我見到不少有識之士針對他的herd immunity去解讀，落注腳研究，初初的我也是，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">近來多讀史哲的我學懂了更大的宏觀格局看事。</span></strong>一個一流的政客是不可能不知herd immunity有多大震憾效果，尤其是他是處理脫歐的旗手。別人以為他搞焦土、技窮，其實他是擺空城，讓最毒的人外逃，順便大量減少人口流動。人一少了，入口流動減低了，防疫仗就易打了，城市負荷也減少，一有爆發苗頭就更易定點擊破。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_733207_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_733207_0&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq2lQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=5995897b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_733207_0&h=bb80d6d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_733207_0</a><br />\n<br />\n根據渾水邏輯，原來好多連登仔都識用&lsquo;更大的宏觀格局看事&rsquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早一星期連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[黑暗兵法]boris johnson智商堪比水鏡八奇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1930886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1930886</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f19f9528ffe845e6ee0bc653ea4dff4912379336","tid":1947367,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"Btw黑天鵝作者：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國最新數據顯示，該國累計有萬宗確診感染武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 個案、 逾五百人病死。紐約大學知名的風險工程名譽教授塔雷伯 (Nassim Nicholas Taleb) 與新英格蘭複雜系統研究所總監 Yaneer Bar-Yam 周三 (25/3) 在《衛報》撰文，批評英國在建模預測與決策上都犯錯，導致 COVID-19 不斷在該國蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯該文指，政府都依賴流行病學模型預測疫情，判斷應採取甚麼措施抗疫。兩位學者解釋，在模型進行模擬前，先要輸入準確前設資料才會得出結果，才可得出最佳的政策建議。如這些前設錯誤，又或未經測試就放入模型，在學術層面上可引起學界討論，並無太大問題。然而，以有缺陷的學術模型制定抗疫措施，損失的卻是人命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/武漢肺炎-英近萬人確診數百死-黑天鵝-知名學者斥約翰遜政府依賴有缺陷學術模型\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%8B%B1%E8%BF%91%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E6%AD%BB-%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%A9%E9%B5%9D-%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E6%96%A5%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0%E9%81%9C%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BE%9D%E8%B3%B4%E6%9C%89%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7%E5%AD%B8%E8%A1%93%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq2lQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=b698fd0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%8B%B1%E8%BF%91%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E6%AD%BB-%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%A9%E9%B5%9D-%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E6%96%A5%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0%E9%81%9C%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BE%9D%E8%B3%B4%E6%9C%89%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7%E5%AD%B8%E8%A1%93%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B&h=6cde027b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/武漢肺炎-英近萬人確診數百死-黑天鵝-知名學者斥約翰遜政府依賴有缺陷學術模型</a><br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯As we said, when one deals with deep uncertainty, both governance and precaution require us to hedge for the worst. <br />\n<br />\nWhile risk-taking is a business that is left to individuals, collective safety and systemic risk are the business of the state. <br />\n<br />\nFailing that mandate of prudence by gambling with the lives of citizens is a professional wrongdoing that extends beyond academic mistake; it is a violation of the ethics of governing.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2020/mar/25/uk-coronavirus-policy-scientific-dominic-cummings\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcommentisfree%2F2020%2Fmar%2F25%2Fuk-coronavirus-policy-scientific-dominic-cummings&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq2lQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=9067a28c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2020/mar/25/uk-coronavirus-policy-scientific-dominic-cummings</a>"},{"pid":"f9d82be866fc9bc07cf3587b168711c37a170a17","tid":1947367,"uid":181655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"寫嗰條友係唔係傻左？"},{"pid":"d7b91002815c919ed160380101571b8e1bbd7c5f","tid":1947367,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f9d82be866fc9bc07cf3587b168711c37a170a17","tid":1947367,"uid":181655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"寫嗰條友係唔係傻左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"至少首相真共同抗疫，同習帝離地指揮冇得比"},{"pid":"bae23d49394d1dc0955b7ce93a5154155d2571e0","tid":1947367,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"曲直難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc404f60e549d32b72fb3d3872d3ae0c634f716","tid":1947367,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9d82be866fc9bc07cf3587b168711c37a170a17","tid":1947367,"uid":181655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"寫嗰條友係唔係傻左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"Boris 點睇都係真柒多過&lsquo;計中計中計&rsquo;計好哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過見佢無啦啦自拋&lsquo;睇多咗史哲&rsquo;嚟認屎認屁覺得好笑啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi